SignEdit: A Bukkit plugin which allows signs to be easily edited while still on the wall/block they were placed on

Commands:
    - /signedit <line> delete - Deletes the contents of <line>
    - /signedit <line> <text> - Change the text on <line> to match that in <text>
    - /signedit cancel - Cancel the current edit
    - /signedit help - Display a help dialogue
    
Changelog:
    1.0.1b: Add a configuration directive to ignore creative mode if a player has a pending SignEdit request, check to make sure the <line> parameter is an integer (1-4), add a help dialogue
    1.0: Initial release
    
Feaures:
    - LWC Integration.. If the sign doesn't belong to you, you can't change it.